    <edge source="Small Prince" target="Baobabs">
      <data key="d7">4.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The prince wants to understand whether eating small baobabs is harmful.&lt;SEP&gt;The prince wants to understand if eating small baobabs is harmful.&lt;SEP&gt;The prince is trying to understand the size of baobabs.&lt;SEP&gt;The baobabs are not trees and are huge.</data>
