    </edge>
    <edge source="Семена баобаба" target="Баобаб">
      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Baobab seeds are the root cause of various issues caused by baobab trees, especially when not managed properly.</data>
      <data key="d9">Изменение</data>
      <data key="d10">doc-1b8b1d20aa2c3a367e6898ef909e1830-chunk-001</data>
      <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d12">1782466820</data>
      <data key="d13" />
    </edge>
    <edge source="Семена баобаба" target="Планета Маленького принца">
      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Baobab seeds can spread over a planet, causing significant harm if not controlled.</data>
      <data key="d9">Вредоносность</data>
      <data key="d10">doc-1b8b1d20aa2c3a367e6898ef909e1830-chunk-001</data>
      <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d12">1782466820</data>
      <data key="d13" />
    </edge>
    <edge source="Семена баобаба" target="Полет в косmos">
      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The knowledge about managing baobab seeds can be applied to understanding and dealing with similar problems in space.</data>
      <data key="d9">Применение знаний по уходу за садом на путешествие</data>
      <data key="d10">doc-1b8b1d20aa2c3a367e6898ef909e1830-chunk-001</data>
